content.title: HyperSpacetime: Complex Algebro-Geometric Analysis of Intelligence Quantum Entanglement Convergent Evolution (Extended Abstract)
content.abstract:
Far from the Madding Cloud

When groups of ants in haystack as agents 
Descending gudied by curvatures instead of gradients
No powerful enough in changing their environments 
Being inferior adapters instead of equal gamers 
Exploring and exploiting various actions
Searching and researching origin of intelligence 
Do they  solar system milkyway universe multiverse 

And the same as frogs in well hawks under sky
And dog's year different to human's year 
And elephant in your eyes not the same as mine 
Human in arbifolds just like ants in hay stacks
Hindsight insight foresight aspiration inspiration passion
Hate bacteria virus war all gone with wind 
No hard times only great expectations
